<gsml:body adPageName="explanationPopup">
    <h1>Charter school</h1>
    <p>
        A charter school is a public school that is exempt from many of the regulations
        governing traditional public schools. Charter schools often focus on a particular
        curriculum or educational philosophy. Like all public schools, charter schools
        must be nonsectarian and nondiscriminatory.
    </p>
    <p>
        For more information, see
        <link:cmsContent contentKey="Article#192"
