                         target="_blank">Seven Things to Know About Charter Schools</link:cmsContent>
        and <link:cmsContent contentKey="Article#70"
                             fullUri="/find-a-school/defining-your-ideal/charter-schools"
                             target="_blank">Charter Schools Offer an Array of Choices</link:cmsContent>.
    </p>
